[B][SIZE=5]Update Log - 28/06/2025[/SIZE][/B]<br>
[/CENTER]
After years of development, I am excited to finally be able to share with you the that Paralake V6 is now live on the server and the [URL='https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3510652177']Steam Workshop[/URL].  Today's update log will go over some of the changes in the map, as well as other gamemode updates both V6 related, and unrelated.  Before diving into that, a quick thank you to everyone who has helped with V6.  From those on the development team, the admins who have worked on updating the guides, and the many playtesters, who have kept the map a secret since last November despite probably quite a lot of temptation to talk about it.  It's been a group effort, especially in the final few months, and we wouldn't have reached this point without everyone who contributed.  You can find the full map credits [URL='https://www.paralakev6.com/credits.html']here[/URL].
