[B][SIZE=7]New Map Information[/SIZE][/B]<br>
I don't want to spoil too much of the new map, as part of the fun will be exploring it, but I will go over some important bits that will help you find your way.  Like in previous versions, the map is split into 4 districts; City, Suburbs, Forest and Business.
