[B][SIZE=5]Shops[/SIZE][/B]<br>
Many of the old NPC shops have been replaced with new brands.  Most of them have also been moved to spawn making it easier to grab everything you need from one place.  Here is an updated list to help you find what you're looking for:<br>
[LIST]
[*][B]Lucia's Clothing Store[/B] - A clothing shop where you can customise the style of your character
[*][B]Hotshot Gun Range [/B]- Like ABlaze-It, this is where you can head to the gun range to try out your shooing
[*][B]Fredy's Bakery[/B] - A small cafe selling food, drink and some baking ingredients
[*][B]DIGIPEEPS[/B] - A tech store, and also a PPS delivery point
[*][B]Poisson[/B] - A place to buy and sell fish, water tanks, and fishing rods
[*][B]Safety First[/B] - A place to buy bandages, medication and safety equipment
[*][B]Hammer Plus[/B] - A hardware store selling raw materials
[*][B]Ol' Stool[/B] - A furniture store
[*][B]Roast Rogue[/B] - A coffee shop
