[B][SIZE=5]The Paralake City Metro[/SIZE][/B]<br>
Replacing the Monorail is the new Paralake City Metro.  It is the fastest way to get around the map, with stations in the City, Suburbs and Business districts.  Look for the overground Metro stand and make your way down the stairs into the station in order to board a train.  There are 2 lines, running every 90 seconds.
