[B][SIZE=7]Adverts & Billboards[/SIZE][/B]<br>
A major change we have made is to the advert system.  To cut down on bad adverts, we have removed the ability to use /advert.  In order to place an advert now, you must head to one of two locations on the map; the Paralake News Building in the City, or the PLN News Stand in the Business District.  From these locations you will be able to either place a single advert, or schedule a set of repeating adverts to go out over a specified period of time.
