[B][SIZE=7]Robbing the Bank[/SIZE][/B]<br>
With V6, XQ Bank and the surrounding area has been remade from scratch. Along with this some changes have been made to how the bank robbery works. We hope this will bring some new gameplay opportunities while feeling more balanced and being less disruptive to the City. This should provide new challenges to both the robbers and police with a greater emphasis on strategy and communication.
<br>
<br>
[IMG size="3440x1440"]https://files.perpheads.com/wC4xcPfTVIgJY4Cg.jpg[/IMG]<br>
[LIST]
[*]Added new lighting and sound effects to the bank when the alarm triggers
[*]The front entrances of the bank and all windows will now be shuttered closed when the alarm triggers
[*]Restricted the bank robbery area to within the bank itself
[*]Added escape tunnel with multiple exits usable after opening the vault door
[LIST]
[*]The exit to the beach will need to be lockpicked by the robbers
[*][SPOILER="Escape Tunnel"][IMG size="3440x1440"]https://files.perpheads.com/dXswqTDu1ASfshnf.jpg[/IMG][/SPOILER]
[/LIST]
<br>
<br>
[B][SIZE=7]Weather & Seasons[/SIZE][/B]<br>
The weather system has received a massive overhaul and is being reintroduced with V6. The visual effects have been completely redone to both look and perform better and are accompanied by new (more satisfying) sound effects. Along with this, a new seasons system has been added which will adjust the textures and models of the map's foliage throughout the in-game year. Together these changes should make the map feel much more alive and dynamic.
