[B][SIZE=7]Interactive Map[/SIZE][/B]<br>
A new map is being intoduced at [URL]https://www.paralakev6.com/map[/URL].  This new interactive web map will allow you to get a better understanding of the layout for V6, as it contains information on all the key locations.  The mugging map has also been integrated into it, instead of being an image on help.perpheads.com.  On top of this you can also find other layers, such as street names and property boundaries.  To switch between layers, click the button in the bottom right of the page.
